nodes.id: h'literal(type('xsd:string', 'ControlDevice is a specialization of ControlStructure-Physical and PhysicalDevice. Each instance of ControlDevice is a device whose primaryFunction is to control the behavior/functioning/properties of another thing (usually another instance of PhysicalDevice). Obvious instances of ControlDevice include: the remote control for one's TV (an instance of RemoteControlDevice), the brake pedal on one's car (an instance of Pedal-ControlDevice), the light switch on one's bedroom wall (an instance of ElectricalSwitch); a less obvious instance of ControlDevice is HooverDam (an instance of Dam).'))'
